We've got one more, here.

00:44:09.360 --> 00:44:11.340
AUDIENCE: I'm introducing
my four-year-old son to

00:44:11.340 --> 00:44:11.810
"Animaniacs"--

00:44:11.810 --> 00:44:15.010
sort of a high point for puns
in my entertainment.

